6. Implementation Details

6.1 Elephanta Vox API

/elephant/trumpet
  - message: text
  - amplitude: {low, medium, high, stampede}
  - channels: [github, tiktok, reddit, arxiv, web]
  - metadata: {title, tags, og:image, description}

Returns: SEO-optimized artifact + cross-link plan


⸻

6.2 Elephant Memory Retrieval

/elephant/recall
  - query: text or concept
  - depth: 1–∞ (default = 7)
  - continuity_map: bool

Returns: all related Pantheon artifacts + chain of memory


⸻

6.3 Elephant Footprint Generator

/elephant/footprint
  - artifact_id
  - style: {diffusion, authority, evergreen}

Returns: graph stamp + index packet


⸻

7. Proof of System Cohesion

Theorem: Elephanta Vox guarantees asymptotic non-forgetting and asymptotic non-silence.
	1.	Memory floor ε ensures no artifact disappears.
	2.	TGF ensures any sufficiently relevant artifact gets amplified.
	3.	EFDK ensures long-term discoverability.
	4.	DFM ensures cross-platform propagation.

Thus PantheonOS has a persistent presence in the digital domain.

